data.message: Ran SuperAGI agent race experiment: Music to Africa path discovery: Team B won (Africa→Music via Afrobeat/Fela Kuti) with 3 hops in ~5 seconds. Team A found 4-hop path via Jazz/Blues. Both beat the API which failed after 15.5 seconds exploring 243 topics. Proved that semantic bidirectional search is superior to blind BFS.
